thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town issues 2018 first tranche corporate bonds worth 3.5 bln yuan

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town issues 2018 first tranche corporate bonds worth 3.5 bln yuan

organizations.name: shenzhen overseas chinese town co ltd

text:
Jan 22(Reuters) - Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town Co Ltd
* Says it issues 5-year 2018 first tranche corporate bonds worth 2.5 billion yuan with coupon rate of 5.59 percent, and issues 7-year 2018 first tranche corporate bonds worth 1 billion yuan with coupon rate of 5.7 percent
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/GuJCgL
